How-to Install:
---------------

# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/egulhan/dotvim.git ~/.vim

# Create symbolic link for .vimrc
ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

# Install submodules
cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

# Install ctags for taglist plugin
sudo apt-get install exuberant-ctags


FAQ:
----
Q. I'm getting this error "Taglist: Exuberant ctags (http://ctags.sf.net) not found in PATH. Plugin is not loaded.". What is this about?

~/.vim/plugin/taglist.vim plugin requires ctags. To solve the problem: sudo apt-get install exuberant-ctags
